scriptname JDLevitationWeakScript

float secPassed

begin ScriptEffectStart

	if JDLevitationData.OBSEinstalled == 0
		MessageBox "JDLevitation requires OBSE v20 or later to run"
		return
	endif

	if Player.GetInCell Mournhold || Player.GetInCell SothaSSil
		Message "Your levitation spell doesn't work in this place"
		return
	endif

	set JDLevitationData.accFact to JDLevitationData.accBaseFact * JDLevitationData.accWeakFact
	set JDLevitationData.dampFact to JDLevitationData.dampBaseFact

	Call JDLevitate 1 0

end


begin ScriptEffectUpdate

	if Player.GetInCell Mournhold || Player.GetInCell SothaSSil
		return
	endif

	set secPassed to ScriptEffectElapsedSeconds 
	Call JDLevitate 0 secPassed

end
